nn.com/2024/05/26/entertainment/north-west-lion-king-performance/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CNN</a>报道，《好莱坞露天剧场的狮子王》是计划在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney">Disney+</a>上上映的一部分，但目前尚未确定上映日期。</p><p>三月，西北宣布她正在制作她的首张专辑，名为“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-and-kim-kardashians-daughter-north-west-announces-debut-album-3599665">Elementary School Dropout</a> ”，参考了她父亲 Kanye West 2004 年的首张专辑“The College Dropout”。这张专辑的发行日期尚未公布。</p><p> North West 在 Kanye 的“Vultures 2”聆听派对上宣布了这张专辑。在此之前，韦斯特为“Vultures”歌曲“Talking”录制了一首说唱诗， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kanye-west-and-daughter-north-perform-talking-together-in-paris-for-the-first-time-3593655">并与她的父亲叶在巴黎一起表演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kim-kardashian-and-kanye-wests-daughter-north-west-performs-the-lion-king-song-at-disney-concert-3759715">金·卡戴珊 (Kim Kardashian) 和坎耶·维斯特 (Kanye West) 的女儿诺斯·韦斯特 (North West) 在迪士尼音乐会上演唱《狮子王》歌曲的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Slash 表示，在音乐中使用人工智能“并没有真正令我兴奋” https://www.nme.com/news/music/slash-says-that-use-of-ai-in-music-does-not-really-thrill-me-3759692?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=slash-说在音乐中使用人工智能并没有真正让我兴奋Emma WilkesMon, 27 May 2024 08:07:31 +0000 Music NewsNewsAIRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3759692 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/slash-matthew-baker-3-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="削减" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/slash-matthew-baker-3-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/slash-matthew-baker-3-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/slash-matthew-baker-3-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/slash-matthew-baker-3-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/slash-matthew-baker-3-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/slash-matthew-baker-3-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我想不出任何应用程序对我所做的事情有意义。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slash-says-that-use-of-ai-in-music-does-not-really-thrill-me-3759692">Slash 的帖子称人工智能在音乐中的应用“并没有真正令我兴奋”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/slash-matthew-baker-3-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="削减" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/slash-matthew-baker-3-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/slash-matthew-baker-3-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/slash-matthew-baker-3-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/slash-matthew-baker-3-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/slash-matthew-baker-3-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-